---
title: Smothered Pepper Jack Burgers with BBQ Potato Wedges
description: This burger that stacks up against the best, literally: Each bun holds a beef patty that’s been smothered in melted pepper jack cheese AND sautéed peppers and onions. Just in case that doesn’t make this burger a front-runner for first-place, let’s introduce the secret weapon: BBQ seasoning. Some is blended into the patties themselves for smoky-sweet flavor, while the rest seasons a side of tender oven fries. If you aren’t blown away yet, you will be when you’re holding this bad boy in your hands.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smothered-pepper-jack-burgers-0e94b5cf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/smothered-pepper-jack-burgers-5f73549488b7a1671764f362-25038db9.pdf
